---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import Navigation from "../components/Navigation.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="Tasting Methodology | Enoversa">
    <Navigation />

    <main class="pt-32 pb-24 px-6 md:px-24 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <header class="mb-24 border-b border-line pb-12">
            <span
                class="font-mono text-xs text-accent uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 block"
                >The Framework</span
            >
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-light tracking-tighter mb-8">
                Structural <span class="italic font-serif text-text-dim"
                    >Methodology.</span
                >
            </h1>
            <p
                class="text-xl font-light text-text-muted max-w-2xl leading-relaxed"
            >
                We do not score wines on a 100-point scale. Instead, we analyze
                their kinetic and structural architecture using a precise
                3-point index (0—2).
            </p>
        </header>

        <div class="space-y-24">
            <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
                <div class="md:col-span-4">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-light text-white mb-2">
                        01. Liveliness / Energy
                    </h2>
                    <p class="font-mono text-xs text-text-dim">
                        KINETIC TENSION
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="md:col-span-8 space-y-6">
                    <p class="text-text-muted font-light">
                        How much kinetic tension does the wine have? Acidity,
                        texture, aromatic movement, and overall projection off
                        the palate.
                    </p>
                    <div
                        class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 font-mono text-xs border-t border-line pt-4"
                    >
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1">0 - Inert</span
                            >Heavy, dull, closed; energy is static.
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >1 - Active</span
                            >Clear signs of tension and forward movement.
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >2 - Crystalline</span
                            >Vibrational purity, persistent lift and tension.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
                <div class="md:col-span-4">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-light text-white mb-2">
                        02. Drinkability / Purity
                    </h2>
                    <p class="font-mono text-xs text-text-dim">
                        FLUIDITY & TRANSPARENCY
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="md:col-span-8 space-y-6">
                    <p class="text-text-muted font-light">
                        How clean, unforced, and drinkable the wine feels.
                        Absence of distractions (excess extraction, oak,
                        chemical residue).
                    </p>
                    <div
                        class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 font-mono text-xs border-t border-line pt-4"
                    >
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >0 - Obfuscated</span
                            >Flawed, fatiguing, or dominated by non-terroir
                            elements.
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1">1 - Clear</span
                            >Good purity; minimal interventionist residue.
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >2 - Absolute</span
                            >Phenomenological transparency; seamless fluid
                            architecture.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
                <div class="md:col-span-4">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-light text-white mb-2">
                        03. Balance
                    </h2>
                    <p class="font-mono text-xs text-text-dim">
                        STRUCTURAL HARMONY
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="md:col-span-8 space-y-6">
                    <p class="text-text-muted font-light">
                        Harmony among structural components (acid, tannin,
                        alcohol, texture) and between nose & palate.
                    </p>
                    <div
                        class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 font-mono text-xs border-t border-line pt-4"
                    >
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >0 - Dissonant</span
                            >Elements clash; structural conflict or domination.
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >1 - Resolved</span
                            >Mostly integrated; minor structural seams are
                            perceptible.
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >2 - Integrated</span
                            >A seamless, unified structural whole.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
                <div class="md:col-span-4">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-light text-white mb-2">
                        04. Complexity
                    </h2>
                    <p class="font-mono text-xs text-text-dim">
                        RANGE & EVOLUTION
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="md:col-span-8 space-y-6">
                    <p class="text-text-muted font-light">
                        Range and evolution of aromas, textures, and flavours
                        over time. A measure of the wine's potential to sustain
                        a critical reading.
                    </p>
                    <div
                        class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 font-mono text-xs border-t border-line pt-4"
                    >
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >0 - Monolithic</span
                            >One-dimensional; a static text.
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >1 - Layered</span
                            >Multi-dimensional; gentle, perceptible evolution.
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >2 - Intertextual</span
                            >A dense field of references; prolonged temporality
                            and depth.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
                <div class="md:col-span-4">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-light text-white mb-2">
                        05. Emotion
                    </h2>
                    <p class="font-mono text-xs text-text-dim">RESONANCE</p>
                </div>
                <div class="md:col-span-8 space-y-6">
                    <p class="text-text-muted font-light">
                        How deeply the wine resonates beyond its technical
                        qualities — its ability to create affective trace or
                        intellectual contemplation.
                    </p>
                    <div
                        class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 font-mono text-xs border-t border-line pt-4"
                    >
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1">0 - Inert</span
                            >Purely functional; non-resonant experience.
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >1 - Suggestive</span
                            >Prompts immediate reflection or nostalgia.
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-accent block mb-1"
                                >2 - Profound</span
                            >A lasting aesthetic or intellectual event.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>
</MainLayout>
